  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>HUNT ME</strong> is a co-op <strong>horror</strong> survival game for 1-4 players. Gather the ingredients for the ritual, weaken the threat and banish it.  Be careful, you're also the prey!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3026770/extras/8712dd95b8d2aa08d8e5fba8719dc236.poster.avif?t=1772211716\" width=600 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3026770/extras/8712dd95b8d2aa08d8e5fba8719dc236.webm?t=1772211716\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3026770/extras/8712dd95b8d2aa08d8e5fba8719dc236.mp4?t=1772211716\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Gameplay</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Gameplay that's easy to master. <br>- Use your hunter's vision to target the threat. <br>- Move around it or confront it with your infrared light. <br>- Collect the ingredients for the ritual. <br>- Banish it! <br> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3026770/extras/195b86822d501558d744c9611a1934e6.poster.avif?t=1772211716\" width=600 height=170 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3026770/extras/195b86822d501558d744c9611a1934e6.webm?t=1772211716\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3026770/extras/195b86822d501558d744c9611a1934e6.mp4?t=1772211716\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Replayability</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The locations of ritual objects, creatures, traps, safe spots and bones are randomly generated. AI behaviour is influenced by the player's actions and location - they're unpredictable! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3026770/extras/0053c1c4c2f4a2f29ca566e7625d84fb.poster.avif?t=1772211716\" width=600 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3026770/extras/0053c1c4c2f4a2f29ca566e7625d84fb.webm?t=1772211716\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3026770/extras/0053c1c4c2f4a2f29ca566e7625d84fb.mp4?t=1772211716\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Difficulty</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There are 6 difficulty levels and a 100% customizable mode. You can discover the game at your own pace. The highest level requires strategy, responsiveness and mastery of the environment.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3026770/extras/8c1e9d0fad0380043518900ad3d98631.poster.avif?t=1772211716\" width=600 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3026770/extras/8c1e9d0fad0380043518900ad3d98631.webm?t=1772211716\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3026770/extras/8c1e9d0fad0380043518900ad3d98631.mp4?t=1772211716\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Co-op 1 to 4 players</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hunt as a team in multiplayer mode. But don't forget, you're also prey!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Solo game</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >HUNT ME can be played solo. You'll need a more sophisticated strategy. There's no room for error!</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>HUNT ME</strong> is a co-op <strong>horror</strong> survival game for 1-4 players. Gather the ingredients for the ritual, weaken the threat and banish it.  Be careful, you're also the prey!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3026770/extras/8712dd95b8d2aa08d8e5fba8719dc236.poster.avif?t=1772211716\" width=600 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3026770/extras/8712dd95b8d2aa08d8e5fba8719dc236.webm?t=1772211716\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3026770/extras/8712dd95b8d2aa08d8e5fba8719dc236.mp4?t=1772211716\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Gameplay</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Gameplay that's easy to master. <br>- Use your hunter's vision to target the threat. <br>- Move around it or confront it with your infrared light. <br>- Collect the ingredients for the ritual. <br>- Banish it! <br> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3026770/extras/195b86822d501558d744c9611a1934e6.poster.avif?t=1772211716\" width=600 height=170 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3026770/extras/195b86822d501558d744c9611a1934e6.webm?t=1772211716\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3026770/extras/195b86822d501558d744c9611a1934e6.mp4?t=1772211716\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Replayability</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The locations of ritual objects, creatures, traps, safe spots and bones are randomly generated. AI behaviour is influenced by the player's actions and location - they're unpredictable! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3026770/extras/0053c1c4c2f4a2f29ca566e7625d84fb.poster.avif?t=1772211716\" width=600 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3026770/extras/0053c1c4c2f4a2f29ca566e7625d84fb.webm?t=1772211716\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3026770/extras/0053c1c4c2f4a2f29ca566e7625d84fb.mp4?t=1772211716\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Difficulty</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There are 6 difficulty levels and a 100% customizable mode. You can discover the game at your own pace. The highest level requires strategy, responsiveness and mastery of the environment.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3026770/extras/8c1e9d0fad0380043518900ad3d98631.poster.avif?t=1772211716\" width=600 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3026770/extras/8c1e9d0fad0380043518900ad3d98631.webm?t=1772211716\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3026770/extras/8c1e9d0fad0380043518900ad3d98631.mp4?t=1772211716\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Co-op 1 to 4 players</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hunt as a team in multiplayer mode. But don't forget, you're also prey!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Solo game</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >HUNT ME can be played solo. You'll need a more sophisticated strategy. There's no room for error!</p>",
